<hw>Cat"-harp`ing</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>One of the
short ropes or iron cramps used to brace in the shrouds toward the masts
so a to give freer sweep to the yards.</def>⟦br⟧
